name: Widgif º GENESIS
description: 𝗪𝗶𝗱𝗴𝗶𝗳 is my passion project. When iOS widgets came out in late 2020 I felt limited by their static functionality. As a mobile application developer I set out to bring our home screens to life. 𝘛𝘩𝘪𝘴 is my first NFT – a representation of the Widgif logo in the shadows. I'll be releasing exclusive NFTs inside the Widgif app in the very near future. Thank you for participating in the genesis. https://www.widgif.com/
